=Colva Ganv=
Goem hem ek supurlem xar. Hea xarant Colva ho ek sobit sundor ganv asa. Zo panchvea rongacho ani sobit sundor somudrachea dennean bhorlolo asa.
Colva ganvak konknnin Col'li vo Kul'li oxem mhonntat. Hea nusteachea nanva vorvim favo zalem. Pioilem hea ganvank Aldeia De Lua portuguesan nanv dilem mungue “Chandracho Ganv”. Colvacho Gaunkar Colvenkar munn zanna zaunk ieta. Colva hea ganvanchem dusrea nanv Colliam. 
Colvache ganvanchem bountonni anikui sunder ganv assat. Tem zaun asat Banavli ani Barpatte. Hem ganvancho mukhel shar zaun asa [[Modganv]] zo Goeant mukhel veparancho zago zaun asa. 
Hea ganvcho purai zago 598.54 hectres. Hatunt bitorlem 239.30 hectres lokosticho zago. Xetancho ani madancho zago 359.24 hectres. Colva ganvant karkannecho zago zo asa to paryatan sthal. 
Mayache 1635 hea vorsak colva igorjechem stapoun zali. Zantun bhitor Colva, Sernabatim, Gandaulim anik Vanelim hea ganv asat. Colva ganvantlem vaddem nanv zaun as dusro vado, triso vado, Sao joao moll, udgea, bagdem tapem, Pequeno Vannelim, Vilha nova, padre gulem, Kopel vaddo, Ambeaxir, chavto vaddo a and chavto vaddo b, grande vanelim, maddel, poilo vaddo, novo vaddo. Hea igorjecho patronn zaun asa Senhora Das Merces, zanchem fest dor vorsak ietarak 8th septemberacher lagim astat tea disa kortat. 
Hea ganvancho annik ek voddli girestkai mhunnlear Menino Jezucho Fama, Otubrache muinneant monoitat. 
Hea ganvank Mahalaxmi asat zachim stapana 24/5/2006. 
Hea ganvanchem panchayatichem nanv zaun asa “village panchayat of Colva, Sernabatim, Gandaulim ani Vanelim. Hea panchayatichem stapana panchvo abril 1991 hea disa stapna kelim. 
Hea panchaetak ek vanchnaloi asa zanchem nanv “Professor Wolfango De Costa”. Hi vanchunelai trisro febrer 1991. Hea vorsak suru zalim.
Colva ganvant ek daktem nusteachem bazzar asa zo pancheaiteichea adarant cholta. Hea ganvant ek  bolaikicho Kendra asa, zo 1998 hea vorsak suro zalem. 
Hanga don madap asa zanchem nanv lions club of Colva zo 26 Janneiro 1975 hea vorsak uptaiilem. Ani dusrea munlhear Colva igorzechem mandap zem janneir 1993 vorsak suru zalem. Hem dunnoi mandap vaglea vaglea kareiovollant upeg ieta.
Hanga ek khelpacho moll asa zanchem nanv “director of sports ground” zo Janniero 1991 hea vorsak uptailem. Ani ek kaidacho sports club asa zanchem nanv St.Anthony sports club assa 18th Septemberecho 1973 vorsak suru zallo. Hanga sorllo mukhel khel zaun asa futball asa, 
Dak ghor colvanchem, zacho pin code 403708, Colva ganvant asa. Annik Colva ganvant police station, hem suddanni assa hanga shakka assa zanchem nanv “ Infant Jesus high school, 1962 hea vorsak survat zalem. Hea shallachi survat Fr.Alvaro Furtado hanni kelli. Hi shalla ganvechea lokanche soglea bhurgeank shikshann melpak lagun survat keli. Unch Madhyannik Vigyan shalla 2012, hea vorsak suru zalli aniuikui serkari Mdhyanik vidyaloi 1930 hea vorsak suru zalli. Colvanchea ganvak bossi, taxi ani motorclicheo sundha asat. 
Colvanchem sonkya 8900 zaun asa. Tatuntlem 90% christao zaun asa, 10% hindu zaun asa ani 2% musolman hea ganvant ravtat. Colvachem sonkhya samanya asa. Zautuntlem nustekar – OBC asa. Baila Dadleachi sonkhya 60-50% asa. Xikopeachem vorg 90% zaun asa. 
Zolm sonkea ani mornacho sonkea 75% ani 30% asa. Pikavachem, xeta batant 30% asa. BPL familio panch asa. NREGA 247 zaun asa. Kelacho pongodd zaun asa St.Anthony club. Cooperative socitichem nanv zaun asa Colva Seraulim Cooperative society zem 1963 hea vorsak suru zalem.Colvanchem ganvant zaitem rostea asa.
Colvanchea ganvant zaitem log nusteacho xetancho ani paryatak hea dondea kortat. Colvachea ganvchem mukhel fest zaun asa Fama De Menino Jezus. 
Colva hea ganvant zaitem vodd zankar zaun asa zatuntlo ek mukhel dotor zaun asa Dr.Umest Panandikar, tiatrist zaun asa comedian Ambe, Joaquim D,costa ani Philip Almeida.
Colvacho log xit koddi ani nustea kaun jietat ani festa dissani ghara gharani chodchem beef, pork, pulanv ani suasages jetat. 
Colva lonkank chodechem pordesachea cantarem avedatat.
Colvechem bhas zaun asa konkanni ani inglesh zaun asa. Punn chodchem bharatacho log ganvant ravtat takach lagun log hindi uloitat.


